Nice to see you.

189
00:17:44,063 --> 00:17:47,482
I understand you have had a little
difficulty on the road. Yes, sir.

190
00:17:47,566 --> 00:17:49,484
At ease.
Thank you, sir.

191
00:17:49,568 --> 00:17:51,861
There were young conscripts,
