and failed to take cover.

200
00:18:18,514 --> 00:18:21,474
Too bad.
I'm sure he fought bravely.

201
00:18:23,602 --> 00:18:26,521
That's wonderful, isn't it?

202
00:18:26,605 --> 00:18:28,481
Yes, sir.

203
00:18:28,565 --> 00:18:31,109
