you and many of the men.

211
00:18:55,526 --> 00:18:57,493
I'm sure she's most interested.

212
00:18:59,096 --> 00:19:01,389
Just a moment.

213
00:19:01,473 --> 00:19:05,101
We will stand on the steps.
Come on, Diestl.

214
00:19:05,185 --> 00:19:07,186
